Babajide Olusola Sanwo-Olu, the Governor of Lagos state has approved the disengagement of Mr Babatunde Bank Anthony as the Director General of the State Sports Commission. Mr Sanwo-Olu, however, approved the appointment of Mr Oluwatoyin Gafar Bolowotan as the new Director General of the State Sports Commission. In a statement signed by Mr Hakeem Muri Okunola, the Head of Service, the appointment is in line with the ongoing reorganisation of the State Public Service for efficient service delivery, the appointment is with immediate effect.